## PROJECT STRUCTURE — ENFORCED

New files go in these locations only — never invent new top-level folders:

  src/app/(user)/[route]/         → user portal pages
  src/app/(admin)/[route]/        → admin portal pages
  src/app/(auth)/[route]/         → auth pages (shared)
  src/portal/user/components/     → user-only components
  src/portal/user/features/       → user-only hooks and types
  src/portal/admin/components/    → admin-only components
  src/portal/admin/features/[module]/
    components/                   → module components
    hooks/                        → module React Query hooks
    types/                        → module TypeScript types
    constants.ts                  → module constants and enums
  src/components/shared/          → shared components (both portals)
  src/components/ui/              → shadcn only — never edit these files
  src/lib/api/admin/[module].api.ts → admin API functions
  src/lib/api/user/[resource].api.ts → user API functions
  src/lib/validations/admin/      → admin Zod schemas
  src/lib/validations/user/       → user Zod schemas
  src/hooks/                      → global hooks
  src/store/slices/               → Redux slices
  src/types/                      → global types
  src/constants/                  → global constants

