## NAMING CONVENTIONS

Components:        PascalCase          → FamilyProfileHeader.tsx
Files:             kebab-case          → family-profile-header.tsx
React Query hooks: camelCase, use      → useFamilies, useCreateBooking
Redux selectors:   camelCase, select   → selectAuthUser, selectSidebarCollapsed
Redux actions:     camelCase, verb     → setAuthUser, toggleSidebar
API functions:     camelCase, verb     → getBookings, cancelBooking, createFamily
Zod schemas:       camelCase, Schema   → createBookingSchema, loginSchema
Types:             PascalCase          → Family, StaffUser, BookingStatus
Enums:             PascalCase name, SCREAMING values → BookingStatus.CONFIRMED
Query key arrays:  from QUERY_KEYS constants only — never inline
Route paths:       from ROUTES constants only — never hardcode strings
Constants:         SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE → MAX_FILE_SIZE_MB

