## TYPESCRIPT — STRICT

- strict: true — no any, no type assertions without comment, no non-null assertions
- All component props: named interface above component → FamilyCardProps
- All API return types: explicitly typed — never infer from any
- All form values: z.infer<typeof schema> — never manually typed separately
- All event handlers: use React types → React.ChangeEvent<HTMLInputElement>
- All children: React.ReactNode — never JSX.Element or any
- Never use object as a type — define the shape

