## COMPONENTS

### Rules
  - Functional components only — no class components
  - One default export per file = the component
  - Props interface defined above component in same file
  - No prop drilling beyond 2 levels — use store or context
  - No API calls in components — use React Query hooks
  - No business logic in components — hooks or utils
  - Max file length: 200 lines — extract sub-components if longer

### Component checklist — every data-dependent component needs:
  - Loading state → LoadingSkeleton variant
  - Error state → ErrorState with retry
  - Empty state → EmptyState with CTA
  - Never render "nothing" for these states — always show something meaningful

### shadcn/ui usage
  - Use shadcn components from src/components/ui/ — never edit these files directly
  - Extend by wrapping, not by modifying source
  - CORRECT:   <Button className="w-full" {...props} />  (new wrapper component)
  - INCORRECT: edit src/components/ui/button.tsx

### Existing components — respect these
  - src/components/shared/: existing components are stable — extend, don't replace
  - src/components/user/cafeFood/, classes/, events/, etc.: working UI — do not rewrite
  - src/components/admin/AdminHeader.tsx, AdminSidebar.tsx: update (add nav items), don't replace

